description: Gets the accessProfile for the specified role name of the managed cluster with a specified resource group and name.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

resource_name.description: The name of the managed cluster resource.

role_name.description: The name of the role for managed cluster accessProfile resource.
